  "name": "DopplerSim DAMU Dataset Collection",
  "description": "Vehicle acoustics and Doppler-based speed estimation dataset collection containing RealData, SimulatedData, ExtendedSimulatedData, Benchmarks, Benchmarks(Noise), and CustomWhiteboardPath subsets.",
